{"tid":2094054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尹兆堅踢保 轟警濫暴","createTime":"2020-07-04T09:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T10:43:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"28c4b65c443947469d2f86e6362afec677b5ea50","tid":2094054,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:42:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200704/FTBIIZS4OJ32XFYXISO352MMFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200704%2FFTBIIZS4OJ32XFYXISO352MMFQ%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=4b7efc66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200704%2FFTBIIZS4OJ32XFYXISO352MMFQ%2F&h=eb89384f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200704/FTBIIZS4OJ32XFYXISO352MMFQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅踢保 轟警濫暴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jx4aBu-Y5DdksGcfaCJqirEwiSw=/190x139/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FTYRGBX7LAGAPM4BAJV4MAICL4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fjx4aBu-Y5DdksGcfaCJqirEwiSw%3D%2F190x139%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFTYRGBX7LAGAPM4BAJV4MAICL4.gif&h=5e2a6044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尹兆堅在醫院外向記者展示被毀眼鏡。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主黨立法會議員尹兆堅7.1下午在銅鑼灣東角道，用揚聲器與驅趕市民的警員理論，卻被指涉嫌阻差辦公，遭警方以胡椒噴劑直射臉部並制服在地，最後被反綁雙手帶走。尹感胸口受壓及呼吸困難須送院，至昨日踢保獲釋，並在被捕後逾56小時出院。他批評警方拘捕他是「莫須有」，反映當局在港版國安法生效後更肆無忌憚濫捕，相信自己的例子只是冰山一角。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：被告多處骨折缺席聆訊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遭壓背拗手 現心律不正<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n「佢哋好大力，我越用力或叫痛，佢哋就越要壓住我，仲要紮起我雙手。我同佢講隻手好痛，唔好再拗啦，佢再拗多幾吓，有警員仲話『好舒服呀，好舒服』，極之離譜。」<br />\n<br />\n尹續指當時<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n直言「好似打風咁」。<br />\n<br />\n被扣查期間，尹表示不適要求送院檢查，但被拖延三小時才獲送院，「三個鐘頭我提出三次要求，佢先送我入院，係好離譜嘅延誤。」尹指自己出現心律不正及心電圖不尋常，留醫期間經多次檢查。他已踢保獲釋，<br />\n。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a0195a9571a054aeba1624ddadf62c9893dcdf36","tid":2094054,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:43:34.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲，但又唔會私人檢控"}]}